  <brief_title>Effect of Sipjeondaebo-tang for Cancer Related Anorexia in Cancer Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Sipjeondaebo-tang for Cancer Related Anorexia in Cancer Patients: A Randomized Double Blinded Placebo Controlled Pilot Study</official_title>
