  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine efficacy and safety of Sipjeondaebo-tang for Cancer patients suffering from
      anorexia after chemotherapy. Sipjeondaebo-tang will be administered for 4 weeks, 3 times per
      day after a meal. Changes of FAACT scale, Anorexia VAS, Weight, BMI, Clinical laboratory test
      such as ACTH, Cortisol, Chrelin, IL-6, ESR, CRP will be measured and analyzed.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
